{"tid":1355041,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"〈藍絲請入〉藍絲之邏輯謬誤","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T21:13:14.000Z","uid":26000,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f6922b67cc504b03179b5e917c1120e3fd8e3462","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"以下嘅所有內容都冇任何人身攻擊成份 請安心服用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">搞亂香港 搞死香港 咁就叫爭取民主？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">先勿論誰搞亂香港 先講香港點先死</span><br />\n<br />\n邏輯上 藍絲理解成 因為有遊行暴動 所以外商唔敢投資 甚至撤資 最後香港會死<br />\n<br />\n但呢個因果關係不成立 因為外資唔會單單因為遊行示威而放棄對香港投資<br />\n<br />\n香港經歷過金融風暴 金融海嘯 沙士 佔中 死唔去不突止 仲可如此頑強地頂住亞洲金融中心嘅地位 原因唔係國內同胞救濟香港 而係香港呢個地方仲有一個好大嘅核心價值 令外商會放心投資落香港<br />\n<br />\n呢個核心價值 叫做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">司法獨立</span></span>冇左佢 香港就真係死了<br />\n<br />\n依家送中條例正正就係影響緊司法獨立 所以先上街遊行 要求撤回 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以 你口中話要搞死香港果班先最唔想香港死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">一班搞事嘅人想藉機搞亂香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">承上題 究竟邊個先係搞亂香港嘅人</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過純粹想搞亂香港嘅人根本唔存在 如果背後有一個可以召集百萬人嘅組織 相信已經可以直接組成新政府 邊有搞亂你嘅需要？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">當前設不存在時 後者已無意義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有人會話係有外國勢力 但如果有？會係邊國？歐盟？佢地同中國有咩瓜葛導致要搞中國？英國？同中國有好大生意做緊 點解要做自己？美國？特朗普一句加關稅已經可以令大陸出現結業潮 何必要勞師動眾搞一個香港 再睇特朗普一直都係以I don&rsquo;t fucking care 嘅態度睇香港 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">結論：冇人想搞亂香港 亦冇所謂外國勢力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地唔搞事 警察點會打你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">此為全po最大謬誤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個已經係基本嘅先後次序問題<br />\n<br />\n一件事總有個開始 究竟呢件事因乜而起？<br />\n<br />\n你冇得無限追溯，但總會有個關鍵位置<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅關鍵位置係林鄭兩度無視百萬人民意 堅決推2讀 然後先有第一波警民衝突<br />\n<br />\n所以應該講嘅係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭唔硬推 巿民都唔會變得激進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時打住咁多先"},{"pid":"56e55af8782af9697d6a4c15d8813751d9e386a6","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"支持藍絲入來即刻駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e13d150f288221076ca7d5446754ecefb89387","tid":1355041,"uid":165336,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"藍屍根本唔覺得政府/警賊係會錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e5cc38575a9f09d4a6f8c25f753652a2cf0469","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f605a803e72bc668b730aac032272841c5745ccc","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5e13d150f288221076ca7d5446754ecefb89387","tid":1355041,"uid":165336,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"藍屍根本唔覺得政府/警賊係會錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"所以我喺呢度直接同佢地講 係佢地思維有錯 你永遠冇辦法叫醒扮瞓嘅人 但如果有一個中立/藍絲睇完寫我寫嘅野 真正咁用自己嘅大腦思考一下 而唔係比任何傳媒誘導 而去重新審視自己一直以來嘅觀點 話唔定會認同我地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7d98f1a1c948d697862247d25e3c8803e921f2","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18086a629855a7c6df0c5246baec308e863261c","tid":1355041,"uid":21920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"藍絲個腦都變哂漿糊啦<br />\n你講道理冇用"},{"pid":"f3fbf7f1c8c7ad3fd7c58cb989d84daf060169b4","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b18086a629855a7c6df0c5246baec308e863261c","tid":1355041,"uid":21920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"藍絲個腦都變哂漿糊啦<br />\n你講道理冇用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我相信有倖存者嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12600cb54855c8dc4cf68ffd64aa6001836779a2","tid":1355041,"uid":285746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340e7524c74cd0085b2e27a33b98e62aac58d49a","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecfb7fed132e21165e0c4faa32b15d182d8ebf65","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"3a48f45764f92aef65e3dfcca48bbe1835e0b590","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"推比藍絲睇"},{"pid":"3dfcd72b0b6dab3bd6fea1f875457c91448c1d81","tid":1355041,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"佢覺得你遊行阻佢佢做生意掛"},{"pid":"d69317b11cc09c32f4b22b221de6cdd4176906a9","tid":1355041,"uid":141914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"1.搞到人地搵唔到食？d人會冇飯開？<br />\n<br />\n2.警察講左清場咁耐都唔走 一清果下又話人地胡椒噴霧 到D警察退後防線 你地又推返上前 咁開槍都正常啦 叫極都唔走"},{"pid":"d9217f6717048510793d33227c227023a4135acf","tid":1355041,"uid":162949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"：林鄭都話壽終正寢 如果你係為條例既 點解仲唔收手？"},{"pid":"965cf9541f1d91ce83005558765535df1ab0e502","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dfcd72b0b6dab3bd6fea1f875457c91448c1d81","tid":1355041,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"佢覺得你遊行阻佢佢做生意掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"同樣係第三點嘅先後次序問題<br />\n<br />\n點解事件會發展成阻到人生意<br />\n<br />\n老董一見50萬人上街就下台 果次夠多人啦 點解冇人嘈<br />\n<br />\n係政府嘅態度令我地一次又一次咁上街 然後先造成「阻人做生意」嘅影響"},{"pid":"64921ff3dd4d4ae808aac8c9af2f84ab7121e79f","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9217f6717048510793d33227c227023a4135acf","tid":1355041,"uid":162949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"：林鄭都話壽終正寢 如果你係為條例既 點解仲唔收手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"香港呢個社會 司法上 用字係十分嚴謹 每一個用字都有明確定義 我地一直要求撤回 係因為條文上只有「撤回」嘅定義先可以達到我地嘅訴求 而壽終正寢呢個字 法律條文冇對呢4個字有定義 換言之 林鄭可以隨意解釋呢四個字嘅意思 然後擇日暗中通常法案"},{"pid":"c4e127b882831cd2be34fe6a3c774606de75280a","tid":1355041,"uid":284672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7435e645af7b493511dc76ea24bb7b4e1e1d1795","tid":1355041,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d69317b11cc09c32f4b22b221de6cdd4176906a9","tid":1355041,"uid":141914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"1.搞到人地搵唔到食？d人會冇飯開？<br />\n<br />\n2.警察講左清場咁耐都唔走 一清果下又話人地胡椒噴霧 到D警察退後防線 你地又推返上前 咁開槍都正常啦 叫極都唔走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"1. 前設不存在 目前為止 1個禮拜上街一次 即係話同一個月一個地區最多只會有4日做唔到生意 如果你盤生意4日冇工作就冇飯開 相信唔係好關遊行事 而係管理有問題<br />\n<br />\n2.清場的確係警察應該做嘅事 不過示威者主要係鬧警方濫權 使用過度武力 唔跟程序做野 eg 冇警示開槍 冇委任證"},{